HOMER V. REED v. JAMES T. VOCELLE, as Director of the State Beverage Department of the State of Florida. 32 So. (2nd) 321

June Term, 1947

October 24, 1947 Division A Rehearing denied November 19, 1947. John E. Mathews and Wm. T. Harvey, for appellant. William Joe Sears and Eli H. Fink, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The order appealed from is affirmed. See State ex rel. Hoffman v. Vocelle, Director of State Beverage Department, 159 Fla. 88, 31 So. (2nd) 52.

THOMAS, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
